  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You use the strength Twisted Chakra provides you to propel yourself faster than anything naturally occurring in nature can, going so far as to shatter sound and even crack the air. You extend your arm attempting to Lariat a creature you can see within range. Make a Melee Vermilion Attack against the target. On a hit, you slam your arm into them with all of the built-up force and inertia you've garnered from your movement. The target takes 30d8 Necrotic Damage and must succeed a Strength saving throw. On a failed save, it is knocked prone and Dazed until the end of your next turn.</p>",
